txt.en: 'I must thank you once again for all that you do for us. Those are all the Motes I have for now. Perhaps I will have more soon.'\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Completing this quest will remove 30 Copper Coins of Gundabad.</rgb>
The March on Gundabad has a small quantity of Motes available.
Copper Coins of Gundabad for Motes
'I would be happy to part with some Motes in exchange for Copper Coins of Gundabad.'\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This quest can be completed weekly.</rgb>
Collect 30 Copper Coins of Gundabad to trade with the March on Gundabad Quartermaster.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This quest can be completed weekly.</rgb>
Talk to the March on Gundabad Quartermaster to trade Copper Coins of Gundabad for Motes.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This quest can be completed weekly.</rgb>
Deliver the Copper Coins of Gundabad to the March on Gundabad Quartermaster
